{"tid":274422,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【回歸20年】彭博三幅圖講晒：港被中資接管","createTime":"2017-06-07T09:51:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-07T12:11:44.000Z","uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c05dc6428a52057ed59279d8e5282d4b617ab51e","tid":274422,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T09:51:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170607/large/1496808788_47c4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170607%2Flarge%2F1496808788_47c4.png&h=246ee14a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170607/large/1496808790_643a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170607%2Flarge%2F1496808790_643a.png&h=3fad6d47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170607/large/1496808791_6520.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170607%2Flarge%2F1496808791_6520.png&h=830e38e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n彭博今日專題報道，題為《Chinese Giants Are Taking Over Hong Kong》，指中資已接管香港。<br />\n<br />\n回顧香港回歸之時，1997年香港由本地富豪如李嘉誠、英資企業如怡和等當道。不過，20年過去，中資機構在港勢力與日俱增，特別在金融、地產及電訊領域。<br />\n現時金融服務業對香港的經濟貢獻近18%，報道以建行（939）及海通證券（6837）為例，兩企於1997年根本未成氣候，但時至今日已成為香港新股包銷商的龍頭。報道更以此點題：「Bye-Bye, Western Bank Dominance」（再見了，外資銀行主導的時代）。<br />\n想當年1997年，摩根士丹利、滙豐、美銀美林雄霸香港新股市場，當時新股包銷商前十均為港資或國際大行。不過至今日，香港前十大新股包銷商，有9間為中資，當中以建行、海通證券、農行居前三。報道指，中資大行為搶生意，不惜大劈價，個別大型股份上市，中資行甘願只收半價。<br />\n對比起六年前，香港仍會致力吸引西方企業如Prada（1913）或新秀麗（1910）上市，現時大部分新股均為中資。<br />\n浸會大學政治與國際關係學系教授丁偉，接受彭博訪問時指，中共希望香港人心態有所改變。他預期，除非本地富豪願與中資企業合作，否則其於香港的影響力會逐漸減少。<br />\n掌握財經地產資訊，即Like「蘋果ATM」fb專頁啦！<br />\n<a href=\"http://fb.com/appledailyatm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2Fappledailyatm&d=FvVMZhfIdlWZlsmtfE6PBYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=bdd80094\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://fb.com/appledailyatm</a>  <br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20170607/56794581\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20170607%2F56794581&d=FvVMZhfIdlWZlsmtfE6PBYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=cdbdab01\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20170607%2F56794581&h=d7ee6f7c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20170607/56794581</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2017-06-06/chinese-giants-are-taking-over-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Ffeatures%2F2017-06-06%2Fchinese-giants-are-taking-over-hong-kong&d=FvVMZhfIdlWZlsmtfE6PBYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=83799eed\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2017-06-06/chinese-giants-are-taking-over-hong-kong</a>"},{"pid":"2fe47e9e952ffe63f64ebd1154f1c138080fe3b1","tid":274422,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T10:06:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f95c94301c02a89bfca3a745a54b54b135c65a3e","tid":274422,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T10:09:31.000Z","msg":"五毛：要不是..."},{"pid":"fe20bd3de05d9ebd65011b2d29066d088cd930ac","tid":274422,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T10:09:35.000Z","msg":"預咗㗎啦"},{"pid":"0ed77f0f6209fe3eb9a06da24dcd1acf9c5a4164","tid":274422,"uid":3773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T10:11:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2583ad4aa3755bec20b05fc8affd1ddc8daf705d","tid":274422,"uid":10626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T10:11:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />